<li class="level1"><div class="li"> <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6T8axj-hMxc&amp;feature=related" class="urlextern" title="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6T8axj-hMxc&amp;feature=related"  rel="nofollow">Generating IC physical layout automatically Part 1</a></div>
